  <description><![CDATA[<p>See the stars of Italy on this ten-day tour of Venice, Florence and Rome. Begin in the magical archipelago of Venice where you’ll get to know the city, learn about its history and sample its food and its wine. Next you’ll head through the rolling Tuscan hills towards Florence where you’ll experience the local delicacies. The tour will then lead you to Rome, a centre of culture and religion, where you’ll explore the iconic sights as well as treasures slightly off the beaten track.</p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>26</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/discover-venice-florence-rome-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/discover-venice-florence-rome-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/discover-venice-florence-rome-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/discover-venice-florence-rome-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/discover-venice-florence-rome-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
